      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the advice. i already tried the steam thing and it didnt really help much with the pressure. i was really hoping for something a bit stronger to get this under control so i can actually sleep. if the cipro is a no go, is there like a standard decongestant i can get at the pharmacy? i've heard of Sudafed (pseudoephedrine) but i wasn't sure if that's okay for being in my second trimester?",
